  "body": "### Proposed Change\n\nShall we consider impose a rule that for when a last-call EIP changes a lot, they shall not [go to Final in that same commit](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/5385/files) and, maybe, revert to Review to give people more time for reviewing the updated version. \r\n\r\nThis issue was inspired in https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/issues/6128",
